I want to make sure my account is live and active. I'm still waiting for my ad to be approved

Hi there! If your ad is pending due to your account being new and not yet verified, please provide the following details by emailing adsupport@newsbreak.com with the subject line: Business Verification –
- Company's full address
- Company's legal entity name
- Company's EHID or DUNS number
- Primary contact person's name
- Company's phone number
Once we receive this information, we will conduct a thorough review and update you on your account status. We appreciate your cooperation in maintaining a secure and compliant advertising environment for all our partners. If you have any questions, please don't hesitate to reach out.
what is the status of my account

Hi Javier, to check the status of your account, please email adsupport@newsbreak.com with your account details. They will be able to provide you with the most accurate information regarding your account status.
